# {{name}}

A Portunus extension scaffolded with `portunus ext new`.

## Develop

```bash
rustup target add wasm32-unknown-unknown   # once
cargo build --release
cp target/wasm32-unknown-unknown/release/{{crate_name}}.wasm extension.wasm
portunus ext dev .                          # link into Portunus + auto-reload
```

Enable the extension once in Portunus Settings → Extensions, then type
`{{name}} ` in the launcher.

## Ship

```bash
portunus ext pack .    # builds {{name}}.portext + prints its sha256
```

Users install the `.portext` from Settings → Extensions → Install.
